<div class="app-card-container">
	<div class="card">
		<h1>About Me</h1>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-4">
				<%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt:"Profile Image", class: 'profile-image' %>

				<div class="skills">
					<% @skills.each do |skill| %>
						<div class="skill">
							<h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
							<div class="progress">
								<div
									class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
									role="progressbar"
									aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
									aria-valuemax="100"
									style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
								></div>
							</div>
						</div>
					<% end %>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-8">
				<p>It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout. The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution.</p>

				<p>It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout. The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution.</p>

				<p>
					<button
						class="btn btn-primary"
						type="button"
						data-toggle="collapse"
						data-target="#jobHistory"
						aria-expended="false"
						aria-controler="jobHistory"	
					>
						Job History
					</button>

					<button
						class="btn btn-primary"
						type="button"
						data-toggle="collapse"
						data-target="#education"
						aria-expended="false"
						aria-controler="education"
					>	Education
					</button>
				</p>


				<p>
					<div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
						<div class="card card-block">
							Job 1
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							Job 1
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="collapse" id="education">
						<div class="card card-block">
							College
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							School 1
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							School 2
						</div>
					</div>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>


